'''''Rhodocollybia maculata''''', common name '''Spotted Toughshank''', is a species of [[fungus]] in the [[Marasmiaceae]] family of [[mushroom]]s.<ref>[http://www.mushroomexpert.com/rhodocollybia_maculata.html Rhodocollybia maculata (MushroomExpert.Com)<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref><ref name=autogenerated1>[http://www.mykoweb.com/CAF/species/Rhodocollybia_maculata.html California Fungi: Rhodocollybia maculata<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>

==Edibility==
This species is inedible, and usually bitter.<ref name=autogenerated1 />
